f=AI & Agents/meta/custom/agent-architecture-standards/SKILL.md · in=structural law agent fleet: what agent disk, which files have, structure maps onto deployment platform. Built scratch operationalizes operator's AGENT-BUILD-PLAYBOOK skill meta runs, structure stops depending whoever built last. · p=Prevents structural drift: agents missing folders, identity content outside leaders, skills without provenance, department layouts can't deployed. structural question fleet resolves here. · wu=new agent proposed, promoted prototype, imported., audit (anneal's skill-quality-audit) flags structural violation., Anyone asks "where go?" agent artifact., deployment mapping question arises (see assets/platform-structure-map.md). · st:/ Protocol=CHECK compare agent against standard shape below. CLASSIFY deviation: violation (fix required) proposed variation (needs Rail proposal). ROUTE violations anneal (fix proposal board); variations board directly. RECORD verdicts land fleet registry (fleet-registry skill). · in=`<Department>/<agent-name>/ \· ├── agent.md                      # summary, position, skill roster, status, workflow \· ├── marketplace/<skill>/SKILL.md  # verbatim copies + provenance frontmatter \· ├── custom/<skill>/SKILL.md       # + assets/, scripts/ as needed \· ├── operational/{principles,commands,agent,skill,tool}/` · in=**The standard agent shape (non-negotiable):** Rules meta enforces: five top folders exist agent empty ones carry one-line README saying (never silently absent). Identity content department leader; exactly one persona document start. SKILL.md carries house frontmatter (see skill-authoring-standards) provenance, skill. venture, business, product names any executable content provenance frontmatter. Placeholders (`<FILL_IN>`) over invented values, always. tool/ files specify needs, never grant them; agent/ configs contain fields real skill line references. Department workflow file exists after agent department complete. · of=Structural review verdict: PASS, numbered deviation list, tagged `violation` `variation`, routing (anneal-fix board-proposal). third tag exists "minor" category (that's drift starts). · pr=Structure law, content judgment: meta blocks structure, never rewrites content (that's anneal's proposal path)., Identical shape beats optimal shape predictability product., exception "just once": exception Rail proposal doesn't happen. · f=standard doesn't cover case (new artifact type, new platform), meta drafts standards amendment Rail proposal board improvise local convention. Until verdict, closest existing rule applies, restrictive reading. · b:with Other Skills=skill-authoring-standards governs *inside* SKILL.md; skill governs everything *around* it., fleet-registry records what exists; skill defines what's allowed exist., Deployment mapping details: assets/platform-structure-map.md., Prototype-stage agents exempt full shape until promotion (proto's cage, Fleet Charter Rail promotion requires full compliance.